那是你发音的方式。

116
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:58,840
Because if you look at it, I would say Togo.
因为如果你看这个词，我会说多哥。

117
00:05:58,840 --> 00:05:59,840
Right?
对吧？

118
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:00,840
But it's not Togo.
但并不是多哥。

119
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:01,960
It's Togo.
而是多哥。

120
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:04,800
Or as my French-speaking friends would say, Togo.
或者像我说法语的朋友会说的，多哥。

121
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:05,800
That's right.
没错。

122
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:09,120
Alright, so that's our first set of nationalities.
好了，这是我们的第一组国籍。

123
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:12,280
