还有谁？

137
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:06,960
Oh, we have a Moroccan, a Togolese, a Pakistani, and two Indonesians.
哦，我们有一个摩洛哥人，一个多哥人，一个巴基斯坦人，和两个印度尼西亚人。

138
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:09,600
That's quite the array of nationalities.
真是各种各样的国籍。

139
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:12,560
Everyone in my class is from Asia, except me.
我们班上除了我，所有人都来自亚洲。

140
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:23,040
There are a few South Koreans, several Japanese, Malaysian, Thai, Singaporean, Filipino, Kazakhstani,
有几个韩国人，几个日本人，马来西亚人，泰国人，新加坡人，菲律宾人，哈萨克斯坦人，

141
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,040
and one Russian.
还有一个俄罗斯人。

142
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:26,560
Well, I think you're pretty lucky, actually.
嗯，我觉得你其实挺幸运的。

143
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:29,360
You have the opportunity to learn so much about Asian culture.
你有机会学到很多关于亚洲文化的东西。

144
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:34,800
I guess so, but I think it's going to be hard to relate to my classmates, especially with
我想是吧，但我觉得很难和同学相处，尤其是

145
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,040
the language barrier.
有语言障碍。

146
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:38,280
I think I might change classes.
我想我可能会换班。

147
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:39,280
Don't!
别换！

148
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,280
Stay the course.
坚持下去。

149
00:07:40,280 --> 00:07:42,600
Your Chinese will be eternally grateful.
你的中文会永远感激你的。

150
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:45,920
